This is a deeply emotional and dramatic METAL-style AI cover
of the classic Japanese song Aoi Usagi.

Original Song: Aoi Usagi
Artist: Noriko Sakai
Year: 1995

Best known as the theme song of the Japanese TV drama
Hoshi no Kinka,
this song is remembered for its tenderness, compassion,
and quiet emotional strength.

By blending its fragile, gentle melody
with the raw power and intensity of heavy metal,
this cover delivers a bold and moving reinterpretation
using modern AI arrangement techniques.

A melancholic metal ballad
filled with sorrow, strength, and devotion.

If you enjoy metal covers, AI music,
or reimagined Japanese classics,
please subscribe to the channel.
